<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>System &gt; Tag &gt; Update tag</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Allows the back end user to update tags.</p></td>
</tr>
