<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>System &gt; Tag &gt; Show tag</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Allows the back end user to see tags.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>System &gt; Tag &gt; Create tag</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Allows the back end user to create tags.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>System &gt; Tag &gt; Delete tag</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Allows the back end user to delete tags.</p></td>
</tr>
